OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FTesco to cut the value of  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FClubcard rewards scheme    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Tesco has announced it is cutting the  
OL,6, value of its Clubcard rewards scheme.  
OL,8,FFrom 14 June, Clubcard points will be  
OL,9,Fworth twice their value when customers 
OL,10,Fcash them in, rather than three times  
OL,11,Fas they are now.                       
OL,13,FThe scheme enables shoppers to collect 
OL,14,Fpoints for money spent at Tesco and    
OL,15,Fexchange them for vouchers which can be
OL,16,Fused in store or for restaurant meals  
OL,17,Fand day trips.                         
OL,19,FSainsbury's and Boots also cut the     
OL,20,Fvalue of loyalty schemes recently.     
